human

Class Physician

  • java.lang.Object
    • others.Resource
      • human.HumanResource
        • human.Physician
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Observer

    public class Physician
extends HumanResource
implements Observer
    Physicians are part of the human resources. They have ah username and hold a list of their current and past patients. they can also receive some messages.

    • Constructor Detail

      • Physician

        public Physician(String EDname)
        This constructs a Physician and adds it to the PhysicianList.
        Its default state is idle.
        With no name or surname specified, its name and surname are the same and constructed like so : "Physician" followed by the Physician ID.
        His ID is calculated by the getNextID method.
        Parameters:
        EDname - The name of the ED in which you wish to create a Physician.

      • Physician

        public Physician(String EDname,
                 String name)
        This constructs a Physician and adds it to the PhysicianList.
        Its default state is idle.
        With no surname specified, it is constructed like so : "Physician" followed by the Physician ID.
        His ID is calculated by the getNextID method.
        Parameters:
        EDname - The name of the ED in which you wish to create a Physician.
        name - The name of this physician.

      • consultation

        public void consultation(Patient patient,
                         Consultation consultation)
        This simulates a consultation by updating the Physician state to visiting, the room state to full, and the patient state to visited. It also implements the HystoryPatients and CurrentPatients lists.
        Parameters:
        patient - The patient being consulted by this physician.
        consultation - The consultation corresponding to the patient.

      • endOfConsultation

        public void endOfConsultation(Patient patient,
                              Consultation consultation)

        Parameters:
        patient - The patient which was consulted.
        consultation - The consultation he was gven.

      • verdict

        public void verdict(Patient patient)
        This simulates the end of the patient's journey in the ED, the patient is set to released (by the physician) and relocated to the waitingRoom.
        The patient is removed form this physician's CurrentPatients list. and the physician becomes idle.
        Parameters:
        patient - The patient which is waiting for verdict
